strings: <voice_0x01000CD1><se_low>King of tricks: Well, it works for some people, doesn't it?
<voice_0x01000CD2><se_low>King of tricks: Without a doubt, Rachapuan restaurant offers great food and drinks! Sincerely, Mr. Todd
<voice_0x01000CD3><se_low>King of tricks: The princess and I are waiting for you! The country's hottest! Medea's story is not trivial.
<voice_0x01000CD4><se_low>January: I understand how my grandfather feels.
<voice_0x01000CD5><se_low>January: Do you want it to be green even though it isn't? Why don't you take them "to drink" to town?
<voice_0x01000CD6><se_low>January: I don't like this look at all. I know how it feels to be discriminated against.
<voice_0x01000CD7><se_low>January: ...Hello, manager! My town isn't far from here. how do i get out
<voice_0x01000C65><se_low>January: Of course, Beckham is no rose garden. However, it was still a long way off, so even a strange old man like me could get in without any problems.
<voice_0x01000CD8><se_low>January: And we probably already know the origin of the dueling magician "Everything".
<voice_0x01000CD9><se_low>January: Some people know everything about everyone. It's called hearts. He is my friend, you know what? Confirm the murder operation!
<voice_0x01000CDA><se_low>January: Hey, kill two birds with one stone! More than a pretty face! Let's go South! Pickham<:> Here I am!
